@startuml
title agda-delta metasystem

skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false

package "agda-delta" {
  component "autoprove.py\norchestrator" as autoprove
  component "scheduler.py\nstrategy choice" as scheduler
  component "guards.py\nstop policy" as guards
  component "goal_index.py\nlemma retrieval" as goal_index
  component "rewrite_db.py\nrewrite retrieval" as rewrite_db
  component "learning.py\nadvisory ranking" as learning
  component "file_graph.py\nproject traversal" as file_graph
  component "agda_interact.py\ninteraction boundary" as interact
  database "data/*.jsonl\ntraces + goal index" as data_store
  file "data/rewrites.json" as rewrites
}

autoprove --> file_graph : project order
autoprove --> scheduler : choose strategy
autoprove --> guards : check stop conditions
autoprove --> goal_index : retrieve lemmas
autoprove --> rewrite_db : retrieve rewrites
autoprove --> learning : rank candidates
autoprove --> interact : load/goals/propose
goal_index --> data_store : persist/load
learning --> data_store : learn from traces
rewrite_db --> rewrites : persist/load

note right of interact
Deterministic acceptance boundary.
No learned component may promote truth.
end note

note bottom of autoprove
Current deferred seam:
richer goal-attribution and protocol coverage
beyond the active replay/promote boundary.
end note

@enduml
